                        <p><strong>ACCOUNT NUMBER / NUMERO DE CUENTA:</strong> 027-014475/4</p>
                        <p><strong>WITH / CON:</strong> BANCO CREDICOOP C.L. - BUENOS AIRES</p>
                        <p><strong>SWIFT ADDRESS / DIRECCION SWIFT:</strong> BCOOARBA</p>
                        <p><strong>THROUGH / A TRAVÃ‰S DE:</strong> COMMERZBANK AG - FRANKFURT</p>
                        <p><strong>SWIFT ADDRESS / DIRECCION SWIFT:</strong> COBADEFF</p>
                        <li>PLEASE NOTE The transfer commission fees are as follows:<br>
                            $15 USD for transfers up to $500 USD.<br>
                            $25 USD for transfers from $501 USD to $1,000 USD.<br>
                            You can include two or more registrations in a single transfer.</li> 
                        <hr>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <h2>NOTE:</h2>
                        <li>Each inscription is only for one participant.
                        </li>
                        <li>After filling the form, you will get 14 days from the reservation to pay the registration fee and send the receipt to wiac2025@gmail.com
